TextEng: I am not a prisoner, I was just exploring.
What is a Master Jumper?
Tell me how to get in, or else you die!
Why shouldn't I just use the rod?
But they know the Big Master chose you, why do you have to have the rod?
Text: "하지만 큰 주인님이 널 선택한 걸 알잖아, 왜 단장이 있어야 해?"

TextEng: That's just stupid. They should just follow you.
Text: "그건 바보 같아. 그냥 널 따르면 되잖아."

TextEng: I already met your chief.
I think I will just kill you.
I think I will just kill him.
I will try.
I already killed your chief.
I will go find the rod.
I think I will just kill you instead.
I don't need anybody.

Text: "하지만 큰 주인님이 널 선택한 걸 알잖아, 왜 단장이 있어야 해?"

TextEng: That's just stupid. They should just follow you.
Text: "그건 바보 같아. 그냥 널 따르면 되잖아."

TextEng: Is this the rod? Here you go.

That sounds like a good idea.
I do not plan to kill him.
To block an entire passage, the rock must be huge! What is the secret to lifting it?
Text: "통로 전체를 막으려면 바위가 엄청나게 커야 해! 들어올리는 비결이 뭐야?"

TextEng: How could you lift the rock?
I will be going then.
I need to get in to see your master.
How do you let visitors in?
Why are you a prisoner?

I don't understand.
Not yet.
I have some other questions for you.
That's all. Goodbye.
What is your name?
<StartCheck>[Persuade - lie]</Start> What a coincidence, my name is Klumph too!
